  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Considering Project Foundations**\n\nI\'ve got a React app up and running, powered by Vite, Tailwind, Lucide React, and Motion. The initial focus is on features for MOVE, the international voluntary opportunity platform. I\'m keen to determine how the current tech stack best enables those capabilities, with specific focus on international offers.\n\n\n**Planning Website Structure**\n\nI\'m now deep in the website design phase, thinking about a home page with impact, stats, and values. I envision bold calls to action and a dynamic mission statement, while the about page will give a deeper introduction to MOVE, highlighting its pillars and structure. I\'m aiming for a compelling site design, particularly to engage potential Malaysian partners.\n\n\n**Designing Project Showcase**\n\nI\'m now sketching out interactive filterable project cards, visualizing specific international opportunities like the \"Malaysia Rural Literacy\" initiative and others in Thailand and Cambodia. I\'m prioritizing tabs or filters for location, like \"In Malaysia\" or \"Abroad\". Each card will show key details, and I\'m adding a \"Register/Apply\" shortcut.\n\n\n"
