        lines {
          text: "    q: \"Who can apply as a volunteer?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    a: \"Anyone aged 18 to 35 with a passion for learning, humbleness, and structured teamwork. For home projects, conversational Malay is helpful but not mandatory. For international projects, English fluency is preferred.\""
