          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    q: \"Is there a program fee? why?\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    a: \"Yes, our programs operate on a strict self-funded model to ensure 100% of donor contributions go directly to building school materials, solar cells, or plant propagation. Program fees cover your lodging, local rural home-stay meals, project insurance, and basic building materials.\""
