    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/Projects.tsx`, which manages the interactive project database catalog for **MOVE**. It features:\n- **Search and Category Filter Suite**: Allows quick filtering of projects based on locale (e.g., in Malaysia vs abroad) or category (e.g., Environment, Culture, Community care).\n- **Comprehensive Project Detail Modal**: Clicking any card pops up a dialogue detailing structural budget summaries, host village names, skills needed, and precise partner organizations.\n- **Interconnected Calls to Action**: Immediately inside the modal, volunteers can click **\"Apply for this Project\"** (which auto-prefills the application form with this project and routes there) or **\"Sponsor this Project\"** (which auto-directs to the donation portal with this target preloaded), creating unified, fluid interactions.\n\nLet\'s create `/src/components/Projects.tsx`."
