    thinking: "**Summarizing Build Progress**\n\nNow, I\'m happy to report a successful build and a clean linter run! My focus has shifted to summarizing the color theme modifications implemented on the website. I have noted that these updates are confined to the CSS, which allows for clean and easy mapping to the Tailwind v4 colors.\n\n\n"
